{"tid":760093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<有片>【嚇呆遊客】難民船登陸歐洲天體沙灘惹混亂 難民四散入叢林逃避追捕","createTime":"2018-07-29T08:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T11:16:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22924d289f1296f49b6a22e85efa4fb0c3ebf4fa","tid":760093,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"繼續有難民湧入歐洲，單是本周已有1,600名難民登陸西班牙。其中周五有逾30名難民坐橡皮艇抵達西班牙塔里法（Tarifa）一個天體沙灘，他們在登陸後立即逃竄，引起一陣混亂。<br />\n<br />\n由片段可見，橡皮艇抵岸前一度被海岸防衞隊的船截住，然而橡皮艇突然加速衝向一個天體沙灘，有難民立即下船並躲進附近叢林，逃避當局的追捕，原本正在沙灘上祼曬的遊客目睹景象都呆若木雞。<br />\n隨著意大利採取強硬拒收難民的政策，西班牙已取代意大利成為最多難民選擇前往的歐洲國家。根據國際移民組織的數字，本年內已有超過2.2萬名難民抵達西班牙，大部分來自北非國家。<br />\n西班牙南部與北非只有一個海港之隔的阿爾赫西拉斯（Algeciras），市長蘭達盧塞（Jos&eacute; Ignacio Landaluce）表示過去一星期已有1,000名難民湧入，形容巿鎮已淪為「新難民危機的中心」，又指人口只有12萬人的阿爾赫西拉斯已無力接收更多難民。<br />\n蘭達盧塞又讉責歐盟對於難民潮毫無作為，他說：「我希望歐盟會針對難民問題，積極訂立一個全球性的政策。今天這可能只是我們的問題，但明天或者很短時間內，這就會是全歐洲的核心問題。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180729/large/1532847779_c6b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180729%2Flarge%2F1532847779_c6b9.jpg&h=5133d79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180729/58496007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F58496007&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d6014309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F58496007&h=45e4edec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180729/58496007</a>"},{"pid":"e31bfb1c21fd52d092fb5aa110ce701485f5b80d","tid":760093,"uid":82532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"甴曱"},{"pid":"4bea0c275b45d4074394d446182350fbde35a24c","tid":760093,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天體welcome refugee"},{"pid":"133f3f9e1611074eeef4700fbd21a8f97f3202f0","tid":760093,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"World War Z"},{"pid":"12b47f78d2d1f5edeaca3ebe05fae524f4f1b001","tid":760093,"uid":85629,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4bea0c275b45d4074394d446182350fbde35a24c","tid":760093,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天體welcome refugee"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"大愛左膠：腳張開 歡迎有需要的難民享用"},{"pid":"3d3522791062ece780f85266ce7c44c1c2a88b00","tid":760093,"uid":55913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"一上岸就有閪屌 果然係天堂！"},{"pid":"9358044bc3266d29a2db90a66266357d8af2b0c3","tid":760093,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d3522791062ece780f85266ce7c44c1c2a88b00","tid":760093,"uid":55913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"一上岸就有閪屌 果然係天堂！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080ba8e05e1e90fabf627644f91a372aa54ec33c","tid":760093,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"又唔知滲左幾多 IS 係入面"},{"pid":"253a0218fd02738fc1ebeebc73f8cae5ec0cd198","tid":760093,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dis